 Consecutive patients with stable multiple sclerosis are being recruited from the neurological services of IMSS at the hospital CMN Siglo XXI over the period of 1 year.

 Of those meeting inclusion criteria, 24 will be selected for the study.

 After signing an informed consent, they will be randomized into 12 for the intervention arm and 12 for the placebo arm.

 All patients will receive capsules for daily consumption according to their assignment, with no visible difference between capsules.

